msgid "Scenario VII: Return to Black Stars Rise"
msgstr "冒险VII：重返黑星升起"

msgid "Sort each copy of Cloister and Knight's Hall into two piles, based on the encounter set icon on their reverse side."
msgstr "将所有回廊与骑士大厅根据其背面的遭遇组图标，分类摆作两堆。"

msgid "One pile should consist of the original versions of Cloister and Knight's Hall, the other should consist of the new versions included in this encounter set."
msgstr "一堆应由原始版本的回廊和骑士大厅组成，另一堆应由本遭遇组中的新版本组成。"

msgid "Flip each pile over so only the Black Stars Rise encounter set icon is showing."
msgstr "将每个牌堆翻面，使<i>黑星升起</i>遭遇组图标朝上。"

msgid "Randomize the two piles so you cannot tell which is which. Choose one pile at random to remove from the game and one pile at random to use throughout this scenario's setup."
msgstr "随机调换这两个牌堆，使你无法辨认每个牌堆背面为哪个遭遇组图标。随机选择一个牌堆并且将其移出游戏，而另一个牌堆则在冒险设置阶段用到。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Both act cards (Act 3a and Act 3c), Beast of Aldebaran, each copy of Tidal Terror, each copy of Rift Seeker, Cloister, Knight’s Hall, Abbey Tower, and Chapel of St. Aubert <i>(remember to use the versions of Abbey Tower, Chapel of St. Aubert, Cloister, and Knight's Hall that were randomly chosen earlier)</i>."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于游戏场外：两张场景卡牌(场景3a和场景3c)、毕宿五的野兽、所有的潮汐骇物、所有的裂缝探求者、回廊、骑士大厅、修道院塔楼、圣奥伯特礼拜堂<i>(注意修道院塔楼、圣奥伯特礼拜堂、回廊和骑士大厅要使用较早之前随机选择的版本)</i>。"
